==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Iteration
<hw>It`er*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>iteratio</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Recital or performance a
second time; repetition.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>What needs this <qex>iteration</qex>, woman?</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Computers)</fld> <def>The execution of a statement
or series of statements in a loop which is repeated in a computer
program; <as>as, at each <ex>iteration</ex>, the counter is incremented
by 2.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Iterative</ent>⟦br⟧
